title: Cockroache eggs
subtitle: The cause of swelling in the girl's jaw is determined to be the cockroache eggs she swallowed from taco bill tacos or licking envelopes. A real medical condition or a trick?
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The reason for the swelling of the girl ' s jaw was the cockroache eggs she swallowed from taco bill tacos or licking envelopes.
